<li> Faye, A. and Fall, A., (2000). &quot;Région de Diourbel: Diversification des revenus et son incidence sur l'investissement agricole&quot;. Drylands Research Working Paper 22. Drylands Research, Crewkerne, United Kingdom.  </li>
 
